locality: Mbeya Region, Mbeya, Naturalized grassland along Kaunda Avenue.
Central Province, Lusaka District. Kamaila Forest Reserve, near rest House, 36 km N of Lusaka.
Kaoma District: On the Kaoma/Lukulu road; 57.2 km NW of Lusaka-Mongu road junction in yellow sand.

Choma District; 45 km N along Namwala-Choma Roads from intersection of Choma-Namwala and Choma-Lusaka Roads, then W (ca. 1.2 km N of Ngonga stream) 2.4 km on road to Macha Mission (Sikweshina) in Mulundeka Hills. Collections on rocky hills of broken quartz in disturbed miombo.
Sumbawanga District, 13 km on Muze road from Sumbawanga-Mpanda road
Choma District: Collecting along the Maamba/Sinazongwe Road, 11.4 km from the Choma-Lusaka Road.
